# AoTv4 custom overlay: .devcontainer/custom/ holds the project's own source (custom Lua
# modules, global_player.lua edits, eq-core-dll source) which the Makefile applies onto the
# bootstrapped clones. Track it -- including the dll .vcxproj that the global *.vcxproj rule
# above would otherwise hide.
!.devcontainer/custom/**/*.vcxproj

